      <mj-column>
        <mj-text>hotels.ng</mj-text>
        <mj-text font-size="12px">Hotels.ng is an online booking agency specialised in hotel booking within nigeria. we market hotels online nd book rooms for clients. we proffer hotel accomodation solution to the people looking for hotels witnin an area or particular city . we
          provide them with appropriate hotels that match their budget and expectations.</mj-text>
        <mj-text color="#00AEFF" font-size="12px">Learn more</mj-text>
        <mj-divider border-color="#BDBDBD" border-width="1px"></mj-divider>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
    <mj-section>
      <mj-column>
        <mj-text font-size="12px" color="#333333">On Payments</mj-text>
        <mj-text font-size="12px">When paying via bank transfer, please include your booking id or name in the reference. If you don't get a payment confirmation message at least 5 hours after payment, please call our support line (+2347008808800) or email us at reservations@hotels.ng
        </mj-text>
        <mj-divider border-color="#BDBDBD" border-width="1px"></mj-divider>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
    <mj-section>
      <mj-column>
        <mj-text font-size="12px" color="#333333">Late Check-in</mj-text>
        <mj-text font-size="12px">Standard check-in time is 12pm - 6pm. Please inform hotels.ng if you'll be checking in late to ensure your reservation is not cancelled by the hotel.
        </mj-text>
        <mj-divider border-color="#BDBDBD" border-width="1px"></mj-divider>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
    <mj-section>
      <mj-column>
        <mj-text font-size="12px" color="#333333">Refunds and Cancellation</mj-text>
        <mj-text font-size="12px">Hotels are settled 24 - 48 hours before your check in date. Please endeavour to call or email to cancel before this time. Refunds on cancellations after hotel has been paid may take 3 working days or longer depending on the hotel's policy. Refunds
          cannot be made on any reservations made on a non-refundable room rate.

        </mj-text>
        <mj-divider border-color="#BDBDBD" border-width="1px"></mj-divider>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
    <mj-section>
