        <mj-text font-size="12px" color="#333333">Reservation & Best Price Guarantee</mj-text>
        <mj-text font-size="12px">Prices on the website are discounted especially for prepaid reservations. Some hotels may charge a higher rate at the hotel if you choose to pay on arrival. Once you place a booking, your reservation is secured, and we'll send you a final confirmation
          on check-in date. However, the hotel reserves the right to cancel your reservation.
        </mj-text>
